📦 Required Dependencies for Jeepmeta Components
These dependencies ensure that all Jeepmeta components behave consistently, render correctly, and support the hologram‑style effects, animations, and geometry pipelines used throughout the marketplace.

Core 3D stack
three@^0.183.0 — modern geometry, loaders, and WebGL2 features

@react-three/fiber@^9.5.0 — React renderer for Three.js

@react-three/drei@^10.7.0 — helpers, abstractions, loaders

Animation stack
@react-spring/core@^10.0.0

@react-spring/three@^10.0.0  
These provide expressive, physics‑based animations for hover, click, transitions, and hologram effects.

Postprocessing stack
postprocessing@^6.38.0

@react-three/postprocessing@^3.0.0  
Required for bloom, glow, color grading, and hologram effects.

Optional but recommended
zustand@^5.0.0 — lightweight global state for UI interactions

gsap@^3.14.0 — optional timeline animation for UI overlays

motion@^12.35.0 — optional DOM animation for hybrid UI